On Escalation Ticket # 00414008 the new comment has been added: Flaviu Moldovan:

Please CC me(Flaviu Moldovan) on responses till Cristian T. gets back.

- Customer Name: Deloitte Services LP

- ACV: 106k+
- Components: AD Sync
- OS: macOS
- EPP Server Version: 5930
- Agent Version: N/A
- Endpoints affected: around 2000


Use case example:

The

Common Name (CN) value in AD will be changed to the global standard of “Last,
First [SamAccountName]”.  Using your account for example, here is the expected change:
 
Before
               alpotter
 
After
               Potter, Allen [alpotter]
 
Since
the Distinguished Name in AD is built using the CN, this also means the
Distinguished Name will change.  Using your account as an example, here is the expected change:
 
Before
CN=alpotter,OU=Users,OU=Practice Office,DC=us,DC=deloitte,DC=com
 
After
CN=Potter, Allen [alpotter],OU=Users,OU=Practice Office,DC=us,DC=deloitte,DC=com"


Thank you!
Flaviu

Please advise.
Thank you!
Flaviu
